  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bb0 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb9\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Emergency phone number to get fuel for tourism workers - Harin",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "An emergency number 1912 has been introduced for drivers and tour guides registered with the Tourism Development Authority to get fuel.",
        "Minister Harin Fernando said that tourism workers can get fuel by calling this number.",
        "He stated this at the press conference held at the Government Information Department on Wednesday 6th.",
        "Drivers and tour guides registered with the Tourism Development Authority have been given an emergency phone number to get fuel.",
        "Through it they can get fuel for themselves. In this way fuel has been supplied to about 1000 vehicles daily.",
        "Apart from this, fuel can also be obtained with a letter issued by the Ministry of Tourism. Some tourism workers try to get fuel by just showing their business ID card. We urge such people to obtain the letter from the Ministry of Tourism.",
        "We think that the fuel crisis will be resolved within the next 10-12 days. After that we expect tourism to return to normal.",
        "Also, since the Nallur temple festival has been organized in August, a large number of devotees from Australia and other countries have said that they will come.",
        "As the month of December is the tourist season, programs have been initiated to attract more tourists during the said period as well.",
        "Tourist arrivals increased by 8 percent last month. Our goal is to increase this further.",
        "I have decided to meet the ambassadors of the countries where the travel warning has been issued to Sri Lanka and discuss the lifting of it.",
        "He also said that for smooth development of the tourism industry, measures to distribute fuel for the planes are being taken in collaboration with the minister in charge of the matter."
      ],
